			<h1 class="entry-title">Why Is It So Hard To Agree On When Human Life Starts?</h1>
							<p class="run-time">12:13 minutes</p>
			
							<a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/scifri-segments/scifri202209025.mp3" title="Why Is It So Hard To Agree On When Human Life Starts?" class="playlistitem btn round red u-noMargin no-ajaxy"><span></span><i></i></a>
			
